data.description: ASSUMABLE 5.125% FHA Loan. This could save you $200 per month or more! Ask for more details.  Welcome home! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is in the District 6 School District and ready for the next owners.   As you enter through the foyer, you're welcomed into the spacious living room that opens into the dining area. Left of the dining area is the updated kitchen with 2-year-old appliances, quartz countertops, and gray cabinets. ALL kitchen appliances will remain with the home.   This home features a split floor plan. On the left side of the living room are two bedrooms, a hall bathroom, and a linen closet. To the right side is a hallway that leads to the owner’s suite and a doorway to the laundry room and garage.  The roomy owner’s suite has a separate walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom that features a garden tub, separate shower, and double sink vanity.  Conveniently located minutes from shopping, dining, and I-26 you won’t want to miss out on this move-in-ready home! Schedule your appointment today!
